title: Mahtay Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Pizza, Western, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee, cafe and lounge. Offers vegans choices in breakfast (tofu), sandwiches plus there's bean salad, quinoa salad, a vegan chicken caeser, and a couple wraps. Pizza and nachos can be requested with Daiya cheese. Hosts live music and art display.
